📣📣📣🎮🎮🎮خود را نه فقط برای بهترین نسخه از سری Forza Horizon، بلکه برای بهترین و کامل‌ترین بازی ریسینگ تاریخ صنعت گیم آماده کنید. بازی Forza Horizon 3، بزرگ‌ترین بازی ریسینگ آرکید بازی‌های ویدیویی بود. یک بازی با گرافیک خارق‌العاده، نقشه‌ای بزرگ، مسابقاتی هیجان‌انگیز و تجربه‌ای فراموش نشدنی در استرالیا. این بازی در کنار برادر بزرگ‌ترش یعنی Forza Motorsport، دیگر عملا دست نیافتنی شده‌اند و قسمت به قسمت فراتر از انتظار ظاهر می‌شوند. Forza Horizon 3 آن‌قدر بزرگ بود که تصور پیشرفت و تحول در نسخه چهارم را بسیار سخت می‌کرد. اما پلی‌گراند گیمز، سازنده سری بازی Forza Horizon، باز هم با جادوی خود به راحتی من را شگفت‌زده کرد. در Forza Horizon 4، همانند همیشه در فستیوال مسابقات ماشین سواری هورایزن شرکت می‌کنیم. این بار فستیوال مسابقات هورایزن در بریتانیا برگزار می‌شود و انتظار داشتیم با محیطی کاملا متفاوت از استرالیا در نسخه قبلی رو به رو شویم. اما راستش را بخواهید، بازی از این نظر فرق فاحشی نسبت به قبل نداشته است. باز هم یک سری شهر کوچک روی نقشه، یک سری مزارع، منطقه‌ای جنگلی، منطقه‌های کوهستانی و غیره، شباهت غیر قابل انکاری با آن چه در Forza Horizon 3 دیدیم دارند. البته این حرف به معنای کپی پیستی زشت از نقشه فورتزا هورایزن ۳ نیست، بلکه این قسمت حال و هوای خودش را دارد. خانه‌های سنتی و مدرن انگلیسی، وجود آثار تاریخی و مناظری بکر، به خودی خود توانسته‌اند راه‌شان را از نسخه قبل جدا کنند، اما در کل اگر نقشه دو نسخه آخر را کنار هم قرار دهیم، با خود می‌گوییم چه بهتر می‌شد اگر پلی‌گراند به جای بریتانیا، سراغ منطقه‌ای دیگر مانند ژاپن می‌رفت. اما این استودیو برای این که این حس تکراری را از بازی خود دور کند، به جای رفتن به منطقه‌ای تر و تازه‌ نسبت به نسخه سوم، دست به کار بسیار بزرگ‌تر دیگری زده است؛ تغییر فصل‌ها. 📣📣🎮🎮🎮🎮🎮📣📣 #game#forzahorizon4 #racing #game_racing #gametime #season#car#gaming #گیم#فورزا_هورايزن #ریسینگ #تغییر_فصل #بازی #بازی_جدید #رسمی #ماشین #طرفداری #رکورد

Já faz um tempo que eu tenho tratado minhas aulas de trompete com um aluno específico como uma aventura de RPG. Eu narro os acontecimentos e o aluno propõe ações. Na maioria das vezes é necessário que o aluno toque seu trompete para realizar essas ações. Tais ações envolvem resolver enigmas e derrotar inimigos. O toque do trompete é utilizado para disparar feitiços elementares  invocar personagens  gerar escudos de proteção   entre outras possibilidades. Conforme a qualidade da produção eu indico se o ataque ou a defesa foi mais efetivo.  A sequência da aventura estava preparada para hoje. Entretanto a narrativa sofreu uma brusca interrupção por conta de uma simples frase dita pelo aluno: Lucas  hoje eu tenho um desafio para você!  Hoje o aluno foi o mestre. Ele havia preparado durante o final de semana três inimigos que eu deveria enfrentar. Criou os nomes  os desenhos  seus ataques  suas fraquezas  as formas de me defender e foi me guiando durante as batalhas. Eu simplesmente larguei minha narrativa prévia e me permiti ser conduzido por uma nova.  Quando eu vi o brilho nos olhos dele com os papeis e anotações na mão eu percebi o quão importante e impactante tem sido o meu trabalho. Ele preparou uma aula para mim  provavelmente porque ele percebe a minha diversão em preparar uma aula para ele. Enfatizo a atenção dele sob meu trabalho  visto que a condução da narrativa  o método de batalha e até as anotações prévias foram um espelho das minhas aulas anteriores.  Ele me deu uma aula de trompete  de criatividade  de diversão  de infância  de humildade e principalmente valorizou todo o trabalho que eu tenho feito até então.  As crianças tem ações simples  mas muito poderosas. Hoje eu pude perceber mais uma vez a importância da humildade  pois ao me permitir ser guiado   pude viver como o heroi da fantasia baseado em quem sou na realidade.  #criança #crianças #musicalização #trompete #musiclearning #musiceducation  #musickids #criatividade #protagonismoinfantil #infância #rpg #rpgeducativo #jogoseducativos #gaming #rpggaming

To prepare for the new Modern Warfare i started off with the one that kicked the series into new heights. Bare in mind I played the remaster version. This is a solid game even in today standards. A short but impactful campaign that has good Characters  great set pieces and tight gameplay. In terms of arcade action you can't get any better then this. The multiplayer is as good as it's always been with the creating a class and adding attachments and skins. There are problems of course. First off the loot box system is horrible. I hate it and screw Activision for putting it in here and screw them harder for making dlc maps for a remaster...dlc. Activision really don't care. And for me I played it through veteran and I get it. It's hardest difficulty but you do sometimes feel really unfair. I lost count how many times I'd fight the same enemy after a checkpoint restart and it always be random if I'd have time to shoot him or he'd snap to me and kill me quicker then I can aim down sight's. Our felt very unfair. Apart from that the game is great and set in stone a series that would make way for a generation of gamers. But what did you guys and gals think? Let me know and I'll see you guys... In the next post.  #game #Games #gaming #videogame #videogames #callofduty #callofduty4modernwarfare #callofduty4remastered

(45) “What’s wrong?” Abram snaps out of his rumination to turn to Cassandra who’s been intensely eyeing him. “What do you mean?” Cassandra  “Is it something that the villager said?” Abram shakes his head  “All he said is that we need to reach his son for a potion that will relieve his wife’s illness.” Cassandra  “Will it require grounded fungus and skeletal remains infused with demonic essence?” Abram scoffs  “The potion is suppose to help her breath  not infect her.” Cassandra  “Then why are you standing there looking so grave?” Abram ease the tension on his face to give a half-hearted grin  “I was thinking about.…about my parents.” Cassandra  “I can have Harding send a missive to Haven to see if Leliana received word from Ostwick.” Abram  “Thank you but not necessary.” Cassandra  “If that will give you a peace of mind to focus on…” Abram interrupts  “Any more news on the horse master?” Cassandra  “The farm remained unscathed from the fighting but I don’t know for how long. Give me a moment to talk to Harding…” Abram cuts her off  “Clearing the West Road will help our soldiers gain a foothold of the crossing. We must do so now.” Cassandra resigns with a sigh  “Yes  we should go.” At the corner of her eye  she sees Lucian walking by. Cassandra  “Scout Durand!” Lucian jogs up to Cassandra and bows  “Seeker.” Cassandra  “Gather the others. We’re heading to the West Road. You should also prepare.” Lucian speaks without looking up  “Understood. I just need to make a minor adjustment to my provision.” Cassandra  “Do what you must but do it quick.” “Yes ser.” Without a pause  Lucian dashes off. Abram trails Lucian with his eyes  “He seems a little nervous.” Cassandra  “I have faith that he will do well. I believe your siblings have been speaking with Scout Whittle by the entrance. What are some of your favourite Steelbooks  I’ve never really liked them until recently  because I like all my games to be matching  neat and level on the shelf and these things are usually in boxes of all different sizes  but just recently I’ve had a change of heart  some of them look amazing and they have some really cool art on them. This gen I only have 3 steelbooks  I was disappointed ordering the special edition of RDR2 didn’t come with the steelbook  that you had to order the ridiculously overpriced version with everything to receive it  as most standard special editions tend to come in one  for example  the steelbooks from this gen that I own; Days Gone  Batman Arkham Knight and Gears 5  were all just around £15 more expensive than just the bog standard editions and all included beautifully illustrated steelbooks  Days Gone even came with a hardback ‘The Art of’ book  which I love. If you swipe across I’ve also photographed my Resident Evil 5 and 6 steelbooks  which I think look really cool! I do have a few others  included in the first pic is my Beyond Two Souls PS3 Steelbook which I recently picked up in mint condition. I also have Gears 1 2  Clive Barkers Jericho and Crackdown 2. But that is the full extent of my Steelbook collection. I’ll definitely be adding to it in the future though. . #steelbooks #ps4 #xboxone #ps3 #xbox360 #gears5 #daysgone #batmanarkhamknight #beyondtwosouls #residentevil5 #residentevil6 #instagamer #gamerlife #gamer4life #specialeditions #gaming #interest #retrogaming #like #love #followme . August and September where full of events  but no matter how late it is from actual event  I will still post some impressions from #gamescom2019 Because there is nothing more precious than to stay true to the geek I am 😅 Unfortunately we did not manage to get into #cyberpunk2077 booth  the line you see is already 5-6 hour of waiting time... but what we managed to see and try out during these two days of #gaming: 1. Pagan Online - smth new for me from #wargaming 2. World of Tanks - our classic  it is already a tradition to visit the booth of this Belarusian gamedesigner :) 3. Humankind 4. Two point hospital - did u also play this gem on PS2 :B suuuuper fun 5. Darksiders Genesis 6. Watch Dogs Legion 7. Medieval - also a cute game from PS2 8. Hands-free gaming- see the video impression  your eyes control the game 9. Biomutant 10. Monkeyking And some other fun mini and not so mini games. We wanted to try out Doom  Borderlands 3  but wait in the line for 3 or more hours seemed too much of time waste  there is so much more to explore at Gamescom  so rather give a chance to small gamedevs  indie village or scatter around the merch area.

This leads me to expect we will have the same map but obviously with altered POI's and new ones too  although you could argue they will bring a new map because they are bringing back old loved POI's (Dusty Depot  OG Factories  Greasy Grove etc.) to bring back good memories we had then wheen we really enjoyed fortnite. Its to try give us the same vibes as we did in season 1 2 3 although it dosent work with some of the things in the game which is why so many people got bored and left the game. I will agree fortnite needs a new start by introducing a new map  but with this happening I don't think it will. This just a theory by me and also remember the gotham city/Batman event is ending soon so complete your challenges whilst you can! . أكثر الشركات التي تدور حولها الشائعات، Rockstar Games وماهو مشروعهم القادم، هل هو Grand Theft Auto 6 أو Bully 2؟ - اخر الشائعات التي ظهرت على الإنترنت وبالتحديد موقع Reddit ذكرت بأن Grand Theft Auto 6 هي بالفعل تحت التطوير الكامل منذ ٢٠١٨ تحت الاسم الرمزي Project Americas، كما أشيع مسبقاً. - الاستوديو الذي يتولى تطويرها هو Rockstar North، بينما Rockstar India مسؤولون حالياً عن Bully 2 للجيل الحالي والقادم. - اللعبة تدور أحداثها في Vice City، والخريطة ستضم مدن ومستنقعات وجزر صغيرة وكبيرة، وستكون أفضل من Grand Theft Auto 5. كما سيكون هناك مهمات محددة في Liberty City - أسلوب اللعب سيكون شبيه بالجزء الخامس، لكن هناك اختلافات ستجعله مميز. تدور أحداث اللعبة في عدة فترات زمنية مختلفة واللاعب سيرى التغير الذي سيطرأ على المدينة والمركبات مع التقدم في القصة. - الطقس والتقلبات الجوية وتنوعها سيلعب دوراً كبيراً في هذا الجزء، لذلك توقع وجود صواعق، فيضانات، وأعاصير. - تماماً كالجزء الخامس، قرارتك واختياراتك هي التي ستحدد نهاية القصة. - كل هذي إشاعة، لكن شي جميل ودي يكون حقيقة، انتوا وش رايكم؟ 😍 . . . . . ‏#iMustPlay  #لعبة #العاب #قيمز #قميرز #تحدي #سوني #بلايستيشن #اونلاين #videogames #games #gamer #gaming #instagaming #instagamer #playinggames #online #instagood #xboxone #ps4 #sony #gta #gtaonline #rockstargames #play #playing #xbox #playstation4 #playstation

. طبق یک اختراع جدید ثبت شده که در فضای مجازی دیده شد، کنسول PlayStation 5 یک هوش مصنوعی نوآورانه خواهد داشت که در بازی‌ها به بازیکنان کمک می‌رساند. .  این اختراغ جدید که توسط دنیل احمد (تحلیل‌گر معتبر و معروف بازی‌های ویدیویی) دیده شد، برای چیزی به نام PlayStation Assisst است که یک هوش مصنوعی با صداست و در هر بازی به بازیکنان کمک می‌کند. این کمک‌دهنده طبق وضعیت بازیکن در بازی به درخواست‌ها به‌ شکل پویا پاسخ خواهد داد؛ به عنوان مثال، درباره نزدیک‌ترین بسته سلامتی سوال کنید تا بازی آن را روی نقشه برای شما علامت بزند. .  در حالی که این ویژگی برای بازیکنان حرفه‌ای بخش‌های تک‌نفره و چندنفره چیز خاصی را تغییر نمی‌دهد، اما برای افراد تازه‌وارد و غیر حرفه‌ای که برای تکمیل بازی‌ها به کمک نیاز دارند، امکان بسیار خوبی است  #بازی #گیم #گیمر #گیمینگ #پردیس_گیم #bazi #game #gamer #gaming #pardisgame #playstation

This is a real photo of Bruce McCandless floating untethered in space.⠀In this Feb. 7  1984 photograph taken by his fellow crewmembers aboard the Earth-orbiting Space Shuttle Challenger on the STS-41B mission  NASA astronaut Bruce McCandless II approaches his maximum distance from the vehicle. McCandless became the first astronaut to maneuver about in space untethered  during this first "field" tryout of a nitrogen-propelled  hand-controlled backpack device called the Manned Maneuvering Unit (MMU).⠀For 50 years  NASA has been "suiting up" for spacewalking. The first American to conduct a spacewalk  astronaut Edward H. White II  floated into the vastness of space on the Gemini IV mission on June 3  1965. For more than 20 minutes  White maneuvered himself around the Gemini spacecraft as it traveled from over Hawaii to the Gulf of Mexico--making his orbital stroll 6 500 miles long. At the end of the 20-minute spacewalk  White was exuberant. "This is the greatest experience " he said. "It's just tremendous."⠀Since this historic first  NASA astronauts have performed spacewalks  or extravehicular activity (EVA) in NASA-speak  on the Gemini  Apollo  Skylab  Space Shuttle and International Space Station programs. Astronauts have explored the lunar surface  completed 82 spacewalks outside of the space shuttle  and 187 spacewalks  to date  outside the International Space Station. A total of 166 hours of spacewalks were carried out to service the Hubble Space Telescope. Today  NASA is developing new advanced spacesuits for use by astronauts as they travel to new deep-space locations on the journey to Mars. The next-generation suit will incorporate a number of technology advances to shorten preparation time  improve safety and boost astronaut capabilities during spacewalks and surface activities.⠀Via NASA#universe_dop #toptorontotech #technology #tech2019 #technews #shotoniphone #huaweip30pro #huaweicanada #pixel4 #techreviews #science #tech #Toronto #space #STEM #computers #gaming #gamers  CREDIT: @universe_dope@TopTechToronto: Your Tech 🔌 ——————————————————— ⁣ Follow @TopTechToronto ⁣ ———————————————————⁣

In un Q&A con i fan  il doppiatore Travis Willingham ha parlato  del Mjolnir abbandonato che compare nel primo trailer del gioco alla base del monumento dedicato a Captain America  spiegando:  Domanda: Vediamo un’immagine del martello di Thor abbandonato. La storia di Thor indegno è stata già esplorata in passato. Cosa rende questa versione unica e differente?  Risposta: Cap è l’unico umano che Thor reputa degno di sollevare Mjolnir  ed ha fallito. Non solo  i “mortali” stanno discutendo tra di loro e non riescono a tornare uniti senza il loro Capitano. Anche Thor non riesce ad assumere il suo ruolo. Farà quindi una scelta molto interessante che avrà conseguenze indesiderate che riecheggeranno per tutta la campagna e si svilupperanno completamente nella storia del gioco.  Il Dio del Tuono ha abbandonato l’arma dopo aver fallito e presumibilmente non si sente più degno di brandirla  scelta che potrebbe portare a una storia che vada a esplorare il significato del fallimento per l’eroe  oppure una sorta di adattamento dell’acclamata run The Unworthy Thor(Indegno Thor). Gun Brothers First Look Android Gameplay ( September 2019 )  The Top Commando is an action platformer that sees you playing one of a number of gun-toting characters. There are different classes  and you'll unlock more as you play along. Whoever you're playing as though  the idea is the same - shoot everything and don't get shot.  You get crates when you complete missions  and inside of those you'll find new gear. Stick it on your team and they'll get tougher  getting them ready for the difficulties ahead. You'll need to upgrade them as well  using dog tags that you're rewarded as you fight.  Different enemies have different patterns of attack  which is great when you're fighting them one on one  but once there's more than a few on the screen you're going to be jumping and running your way through storms of bullets from every angle. Начну с того  что это именно та игра  которая была сделана с душой. Сочетание захватывающего сюжета  в который погружаешься с головой  великолепного музыкального сопровождения  визуального ряда  от которых мурашки по коже  - все это создает непревзойденную мрачную атмосферу. Это взрослая печальная сказка о крысином принце  который всего лишь хочет к маме. О его сестре  которая любыми силами пытается защитить своего младшего брата  пренебрегая чужими жизнями. Об их преданных и самоотверженных друзьях.  Пусть это и сказка  но атмосфера средневековья и эпидемия чумы во Франции 1349-х годов отображены без прикрас  во всех ее отвратительнейших и ужасных проявлениях. Сам геймплей легкий и непринужденный - линейное повествование  элементы выживания  стелса и крафтинга (последний показался мне не обязательным  так как игра сама по себе весьма несложная). #gamer #game #gaming #girlgamer #aplaguetale #plaguetaleinnocence #instagame #instagamer #gamescreenshot #gamephoto #игры #компьютерныеигры #обзоригры

Finally it's #backlogbattler time and this time it's Fist of the North Star Lost Paradise on PS4. A game where you play as Kenshiro in another non canon adventure where knowing characters does help. In the tutorial you take out Shin  then go to the city of Eden where you become it's protector. You befriend the captain of the guard  get a truck you can ride around the sandbox in  do odd jobs like bartending  healing and managing a host club. You get random battles with goons everywhere which build up exp. You get references to the anime and manga everywhere. It's a wander around fighty drivey smash people's skulls in affair that plays a lot like Yakuza. It's mindless and can rack up the time easily. It's a fun game and if you like the series you'll love it. If you allow things to get on top of you however the main story will take a back seat and you'll find yourself just wandering around or driving around the desert looking for people to kill and items to get in the wastes. It's a fun game and I think it's worth the £30 asking price. #sega #sony #gaming #gamer #retro #arcade #franchise #retrocollectiveeurope #pickups #3d #adventure #rpg #action #3d #atlus #fistofthenorthstar #hokutonoken #kenshiro #playstation #ps4 #gamestergram #videogames #gamersunite #gamecollector #gamersofinstagram #jackrabbitgamer

В сети начала появляться новая информация  касающаяся новых игровых консолей от Sony  да я не опечатался речь идёт именно о выпуске сразу нескольких консолей одновременно☝️ При чём об этом говорят несколько японских источников (так написано в слитой инфе)😁  которые могут и вправду писать реальные вещи с учётом того  что выход PlayStation 5 должен состояться до конца 2020 года. Давайте разберём как может сработать данная стратегия на примере прошлого поколения консолей  а также телефонов🤓 И немного истории📑  PlayStation 4 вышла в 2013 году  но через пару лет её мощности уже не стало хватать для обработки изображения в разрешении 4К. Чтобы закрыть этот пробел Sony в 2016 году выпускает PlayStation 4 Pro  которая является более мощной версией стандартной консоли💪  Всё вроде бы отлично  но те кто уже купил себе PS4 вряд ли пойдут покупать себе Pro-версию  которая дороже на 30-40% обычной  так как разница будет исключительно в возможности передачи картинки в 4К и более стабильной частоте кадров🙄  Так вот сейчас Sony вовсе может сразу выпустить 2 версии консоли - обычную PlayStation 5 и PlayStation 5 Pro🤔  стоимость которых будет отличаться на 150-200 долларов друг от друга  но сразу на старте у нас как у покупателей будет выбор - взять подороже и получить консоль мощнее  например  она сможет выводить разрешение в 8К при стабильной частоте кадров или взять обычную версию  которая будет отлично справляться с 4К разрешением. На мой взгляд  данный ход является отличной идеей  так как он сможет угодить сразу нескольким сегментам покупателей👍 Странно  что производители игровых приставок уже давно так не делают  ведь все производители телефонов только так и поступают.  Далеко за примером ходить не нужно  хочешь покупай IPhone 11  а хочешь IPhone 11 Pro  ну либо вообще его не покупай. Главное  что есть выбор  сразу на старте продаж😬 Продолжение в комментариях ниже 👇 #sony #playstation5 #playstation4 #ps4pro #nextgen #gaming #gamernews #games #консоли #игры #игровыеновости #размышления

Es un juego de mundo abierto basado en la clásica saga de Tom Clancys  en donde podremos jugar solo o en equipo de hasta tres aliados para enfrentar y explorar la basta isla conocida como Aurora. O enfrentarnos en modo PVP en equipos de hasta cuatro participantes. Estamos frente a un juego que promete ser la unión de todos sus predecesores  desde sistemas tácticos  sigilo o destruccion. É extremamente comum em um jogo você ter vários aspectos que se repetem  inimigos  objetos no cenário  itens e etc.  Por isso também é bastante comum nós podermos generalizar essas coisas e reutiliza-lás. … Pegue o exemplo de um personagem principal  ele vai estar EM TODAS AS FASES! Kkkk Agora imagine o fluxo -> Criar uma cena nova -> Colocar um SKSpriteNode -> Colocar a textura do personagem -> Seta as animações -> Os componentes -> Roda o jogo  Agora pense que seu jogo tem 30 fases distintas… Isso irá se repetir 30 vezes  kkkk.  Pior… Na 27 fase você percebeu que a escala podia ser melhorada  aumentar só um pouquinho  você terá que voltar em cada fase e ajustar isso  certo?  Pois bem  chega de fazer as coisas no Go horsing… trago a vocês a tal solução… SKReferenceNode Esse lindo  é um node que simplesmente é uma referência a uma outra cena! Então numa cena podemos fazer o personagem principal e em todas as outras 30 só referenciaremos ela. Relaxa que não pesa já que é só uma referência! E você também pode modificar a vontade dentro de uma cena específica se quiser algo especializado para tal cena  ou modificar na cena “mestre” e assim em todos os lugares que ela estiver sendo referenciada a modificação será aplicada! Game eSports  PlayerUnknown's Battlegrounds (PUBG) Mobile berhasil mengalahkan Fortnite dalam segi jumlah pengguna karena memiliki spesifikasi yang lebih ramah.  Jauh berbeda dengan Fortnite  game besutan Epic Games ini dikenal cukup membuat pengguna smartphone harus merogoh kocek lebih. Pasalnya permainan berjenis battle royale ini merupakan perpindahan dari versi PC. Tak ayal spesifikasi yang dibutuhkan juga harus tinggi seperti platform iOS versi 11.  Perbedaan tidak dari spesifikasi saja  melainkan juga kemudahan akses. PUBG lebih mudah didapatkan para gamers melalui aplikasi Google Playstore. Sementara pengembang Fortnite memutuskan untuk tidak menawarkan game buatannya di aplikasi itu karena akan mendapat potongan keuntungan sebesar 30 persen.  Pengguna yang terbilang banyak  tak ayal membuat PUBG bisa meraih keuntungan besar sepanjang tahun ini yakni sebanyak 860 juta dollar (Rp12 triliun). Minecraft foi lançado em 2009 e esse ano comemora 10 anos do seu lançamento oficial  ultrapassando Tetris  que até então ocupava o primeiro lugar primeiro lugar  o clássico de bloquinhos chegou a marca de 170 milhões. O jogo se tornou um fenômeno após o lançamento e até hoje ganha jogadores de todas as idades espalhados por todo o mundo. Logo em seguida  um sucesso atual  GTA V  conta com mais de 110 milhões de cópias vendidas  lançado em 2013  é o produto de entretenimento mais lucrativo da história.  #game #gaming #jogos #thelastofus #ps4 #tech #tecnologia #technology #brasil #br

Alasan utama developer game akan bisa fokus membuat pengalaman game di PS5 menyenangkan adalah karena Solid State Drive (SSD) baru yang dibenamkan di dalamnya. Untuk Sawi dan timnya  mereka harus merancang level game dengan cara tertentu karena mereka tidak ingin terjadi loading yang mengganggu dan ini tentu saja sangat membatasi mereka. **Early Patch Notes** - Content creators had the opportunity to play Apex Legends Season 3 early and this is a combination of observations and patch notes created by them. - May be slightly different upon launch - ———Charge Rifle——— •Energy sniper  takes Extended Energy Mag  Scope and Sniper Stock as attachments •Works similarly to alt-fire Havoc  except consumes 1 ammo per shot  deals much more damage  and... •The initial targeting laser deals small damage before the powerful hit. Up to 75 damage per shot (body) - ———Hop-ups——— - •Disruptor Rounds removed •Skullpiercer Rifling removed •Double Tap: Fires 2 shots in rapid succession with every trigger pull. For the G7 Scout and the Eva-8 Shotgun. (Purple) •Anvil Reciever: Makes semi auto shots do more damage  with a slower rate of fire and uses two ammo. For the R-301 and VK47-Flatline. (Gold) - ——Legend Changes (not confirmed)—— - •Pathfinder's grapple has been altered. The grapple itself moves slower and the delay before Pathfinder moves toward it is longer. (it's only very slight  but will require relearning of timing) •Characters inside Gibraltar's Dome Shield have reduced ability cooldown time. •Gibraltar and Bangalore's Ultimate damage increased •Wraith in phase/portal now takes Ring damage •Bloodhound's Ultimate duration increased - ———Item Changes——— - •Golden Backpack perk changed to Guardian Angel: Revived allies have increased shields and health when you revive them (50 shields and 70 health on revive) •Golden Body Shield takes the old Fast Use perk from the backpack - ———Gun Changes——— - •Longbow fire rate reverted to pre-S2 buff •Longbow and Wingman base headshot damage adjusted to around Skullpiercer level •R99 Level 3 magazine sized reduced from 30 to 27 •L-Star has a new optic for clearer aiming  as well as increased projectile size •All-around shotgun buff  projectile size is larger . . . . . . Per quanto possa essere un nuovo soulslike  Code Vein si conferma come un prodotto dall’anima originale e complessa  sfruttando l’estetica giapponese per proporre una delle esperienze più divertenti del genere. Attraverso a un sistema tanto accessibile quanto profondo e malleabile  vivere i panni di un Redivivo diventa una sfida più che gustosa che può essere adattata a qualsiasi tipo di giocatore. Ma il combattimento non è l’unico elemento invitante del gioco: la trama coinvolgente – anche grazie a un editor più che ottimo – e il ricco cast sono solo la portata principale di un mondo fatto di misteri  ricordi e colpi di scena sconvolgenti. Nonostante qualche comprensibile difetto  Bandai Namco e le menti dietro God Eater sono riusciti a produrre una nuova formula vincente  facendo nascere un’esperienza che si fa decisamente perdonare della lunga attesa.⠀ La mia Recensione di Code Vein per Game Division!⠀ -⠀ -⠀ #codevein #bandainamco #anime #vampire #soulslike #pc #ps4 #playstation #nintendoswitch #sony #xbox #mcirosoft #gamingfolk #gaming #gamer #game #videogame #videogames #videogioco #videogiochi #nerd #geek #singleplayer #multiplayer #player #playing #play #gamereview #recensione

Zelda Link’s Awakening – это ремейк классической Зельды с видом сверху  выпущенной ещё в далёком 1993 году на #GameBoy. На #NintendoSwitch игра перенесена практически с учётом всех нюансов  с улучшением графики и управления. Эта забота одновременно и плюс и минус игры. Бывалые геймеры будут рады и вспомнят былые времена  когда каждый секрет в подобных РПГ решался далеко не сразу и приходилось пробегать всю карту в течении нескольких часов  чтобы наконец понять  что и куда дальше. Но сегодняшние геймеры скорее назовут это проблемой геймдизайна  но никак не фишкой игры.  Что касается меня  то проблемы при прохождении я испытал буквально пару тройку раз. И это не проблемы с загадками в подземельях (они то как раз здесь очень крутые и их интересно решать именно самому)  а практически всегда это был вопрос «Куда же идти дальше?» Порой игра даёт лишь мелкие подсказки  которые не всегда очевидны. Решал это с помощью гайда для версии игры 1993 года (благо вся карта перенесена в ремейк 1 в 1) и зазрения совести от этого не испытываю. Пробегать всю карту и рубить мечом каждый кустик в надежде  что вот сейчас то под этим будет секретный вход в нужное подземелье… время дороже и времена не те :) В целом  ремейк однозначно понравился. Особо хочется отметить графику и стилистику проекта. Эстетика пластиковых игрушек выглядит замечательно  мир и персонажи очаровывают. #LinksAwakening способна вернуть вас в детство  даже если вы не играли в оригинал. А #Switch получил ещё один отличный эксклюзив в свою библиотеку.  #zelda #nintendoswitchgames #nintendo #linkzelda #portablegaming #rpggames #videogames #consolegaming #консольныеигры #видеоигры #обзорыигр #games #gaminglife

🎮 BARCODE BATTLERS II 時空を超えた戦士たち (Warriors who travelled in time) . Barcode Battlers was a series of Handheld consoles made by Epoch. . Barcode scanning toys and arcade games were extremely popular in the 90's Japan including the Datach Famicom add on  the later Digivices and Barcode Wars by Bandai. The strength of the Barcode Wars series was its connection to nintendo  allowing them to make exclusive barcode games with nintendo franchise such as Mario Bros and Zelda. . It also allowed players connect to their Super Famicom or original Gameboy via the 'Barcode Boy' to send data from the barcode cards into the Barcode Battler console games. . Barcode Battler was highly successful in Japan and even saw a release of western versions with alternative art and characters. . One of Nintendo’s most successful franchises  “Mario Kart Tour”  is now available for everyone to play on their smartphones. . While it will be a similar gameplay to the Switch  some of its controls and features will be optimised for mobile devices. For example. The multiplayer option will not be available for the meantime but it is expected to be added later on as an in-app purchase option. . A test version of the game developed with partner DeNA Co Ltd featured in-game payment mechanics including gacha where players pay to receive random rewards — such as rare drivers and karts. “It’s going to be a challenge to apply Japanese-style gacha mechanics in the West ” said Michael Pachter  analyst at Wedbush Securities  who sees Mario Kart Tour struggling to hold players’ interest long enough to sustain in-game spending. It also remains to be seen whether Nintendo will be able to square the use of gacha with its famous family-friendly image. . But for the meantime  the app is now available to download on the App Store and the Google Play Store and is totally free to play! Review Summary- Control ===================== SCORE: 9.1 ===================== You looking for a paranormal  sci-fi action game? This is the game for you! I can guarantee you haven't played anything quite like this before.  It has such a unique style and atmosphere  it oozes mystique  and has a certain stillness that keeps you on edge. It's reminiscent of the old Stanley Kubrick classics  so it wouldn't surprise me if that's where they got their inspiration from.  The combat is some of the most fun you'll have this year. Both the gunplay and psychic abilities are polished and each battle is a thrill. You'll always leave the battlefield in a state of choas  thanks to the destructible environments.  The story is full of mystery and will keep you invested  even if it can be a bit confusing at times  especially with the in-game terminology. Extra lore is told through an excessive amount of collectibles  so while there is a lot to learn about this fascinating world  you're constantly stopping to read yet again. It disrupts gameplay and I do wish it was handled more efficiently.  The side missions are just as much of a standout as the main story  with each one containing an interesting and unique storyline  and I always looked forward to each one.  Exploration was one of the weaker elements of the game  as it did get a little frustrating at times getting to where you needed to go. But this was made up by the amount of hidden secrets (and even some good puzzles) scattered around each area.  While it's a relatively short game  I still recommend this to anyone  as it's one of the better games this year. Ein legendäres Spiel im neuen Gewand – The Legend of Zelda: Link`s Awakening macht auf der Nintendo Switch Lite allerhand her. Spielspaß  Begeisterung und Freude im Herzen garantiert. ➡️➡️ Swipe to see gameplay➡️➡️ . . Playing some Kirby Star Stacker on SNES. I really like how they still went with the crayon style graphics like Yoshi’s Island. Game looks like an obvious tie in to Kirby Dream Land 3 which was released months later. Though I’m disappointed with how short the game is. I feel like it was rushed and not too much heart was put into this. I kind of expected a little more from this one even though we do get a new character Gryll after this title the character never made any appearances afterwards in the Kirby series and recently is a spirit in Smash Bros Ultimate. This version of Star Stacker is rare and is the only Japan exclusive Kirby title we never got in the west. Being released exclusively on SF Memory Cassette carts on the Super Famicom  it eventually did get a retail release but there’s a small about of copies and is expensive especially in CIB. If you’ve played Star Stacker on your GameBoy I don’t think your missing out much on this title unless you don’t have access to a link cable or another copy. But still the original GameBoy port of Star Stacker is much more cheaper and you get to see it pop out nicely on your Super GameBoy.  #kirby #kirbystarstacker #kirbykirakirakids #snes #16bit #kirbysdreamland3 #puzzlegames #superfamicom #kirbysdreamland #supernintendo #nintendo #nintendoswitch #retrogaming #importgaming #japanesevideogames #kirbyssuperstarstacker #kirbyssparklingkids #カービィのきらきらきっず  #カービィ #任天堂 #supersmashbros #スーパーファミコン #ニンテンドー #gameboy #星のカービィ#gamer #gaming #retrocollective

On-going review- Control ==================== My last post before I wrap up my review tomorrow. Now I've been mostly positive about this game so far  but it's not perfect  and there were a couple of things that held it back from true greatness.  I already talked about the excessive amounts of collectibles in my last post. It's fine to have a lot of extra lore  but surely there was a more efficient way to go about it.  My other main issue was how useless the map was. Maybe use it as a rough guide  but not to go exactly where you need to go. A lot of areas are multi-story  and the map just shows everything in one clump. If you're trying to get from one room to another  the map be more misleading than anything  and I did get frustrated quite a few times trying to get around.  When you think of maps from other games  like Resident Evil 2  they're laid out so clearly it helps makes exploration more fun because you're not wasting time looking at blank walls where the map says there should a doorway.  But I will admit my criticisms are fairly minor and didn't detract too much from the fun overall. Children Of Morta es un juego desarrollado por Dead Mage que ya está disponible en early access y espera a su lanzamiento en consolas a partir del 15 de octubre. Esta entrega es un juego de RPG de acción que cuenta la historia de una familia de héroes a la cual controlaremos a través de un mundo generado de manera procedural. Tanto su estética pixel art como su jugabilidad son sus alegatos principales. Primero Contamos con un juego que trae unas animaciones extraordinarias y luego un sistema de progresión muy bien trabajado el cual se extiende hasta seis personajes que en conjunto con el combate que es divertido y equilibrado hacen de éste un juego muy entretenido.  #childrenofmorta #deadmage #indie #game #gamer #gaming #videogame #videojuego #ps4 #playstation #nintendo #nintendoswitch #switch #xboxone #xbox #microsoft #pc #pcgaming #pcgamer #pcgame #roguelike #mazmorras #mazmorra

So I must say  upon initial reaction to the ending of Tag  my reaction in my previous post still holds truth. However. - - After lots of reading  listening to radios  and watching YouTube videos  I can not say Tag is a bad map. Its truthfully brilliant once you give it some thought  and delivers a tragic ending no one saw coming. - - I will however  say that Tag is still a disappointing map to what they were building up. All we heard about since origins was “The Great War”. All through Blops4  it seemed to be the main point of focus leading up to Tag  giving most of us the impression we would be participating. Like I had hoped. - - Instead  we were completely thrown for a loop. Given something we just did not expect. So now this beckons the question  was this a bad thing? I dont think so. I actually think on Treyarch’s end  if their resources were as limited as its been rumored  was pretty brilliant. Because they pulled it off. - - Its a beautiful map. A nice reimagination of Call of the Dead  which really was one of my favorite maps ever. The radios are super interesting  the wonder weapons are pretty decent and easy to get  and it really plays like old school zombies. - - The ending makes sense too. Given all things considered and understanding their ultimate sacrifice  it is actually really beautiful. Its sad. It actually does make you think once you’re given more context. Once you understand  there was no way to end the cycle with all them existing. It didnt matter how they changed the future  their existence as a whole was the fracture that threw the very universe into chaos. - - Now i ask you  what do you think? Happy Dragon Quest XI S Day.🐉🎉🎊🎉 A new amazing addition to the series  or well.. a port remake with an addition of 2D mode + extra stuffs..😍 Its my first time going through both viii and xi . But currently only just started DQ VIII.😁. Just finished vii yesterday and its the most longest for a DQ game ever lol.😂. With DQ XI S (been waiting for this version from the start) out  its finally time to embark on the journey of another hero in another world/Realm. Tbh all DQ games are all kinda have that same thing plot wise  idk bout i ii  and iii cuz never had the chance to try them. But for iv-vii  and ix. its kinda same thing all over again. Just different kind of approach for characters story but all the same for endgame.😄 Each characters are unique in their own ways.😂 Love to see some variations.😍🤣 Now im ready to experience DQ Viii and DQ Xi. DQ XI S is an evolved form of DQ VIII from its battle mechanics and well u start using skill points to assign skills and abilities instead of doing vocations (freedom to built your jobs) for each characters. DQViii was the start of all that where each characters learn their own specific spells/abilities depending on their own unique weapon skill sets that comes together with how each character can handle specific kinds of weapons.⚔🏹🛡 Definitely gonna have fun with both titles.👍More amazing titles coming up in the next few months  definitely gonna check them out. So… I just finished playing my first fire emblem three houses playthrough with the golden deer. The only other fire emblem game I played was fates: birthright but I never finished it and it did not grab my attention like three houses did. What I can say is that I loved this game  despite there being thing that I did not like/hated in it  but I  still loved the game through and through. I know that there are other routes  but I am planning on playing the GD route again and plan to recruit everyone into my house  so I will most likely watch a playthough on the other routes or play the other routes myself later in time. I can honestly say that this is one of the biggest if not the biggest Nintendo switch game of this year and I would highly recommend playing this game. I know there are people who do not like strategy rpg games and I understand that because I do not really like the genre like that  but give this game a chance at least. Alright I’m done talking and I will talk to you all later. . . . . . . . . . . . . Quando alguém disser que videogame é coisa de desocupado  mostre isso😅  De acordo com um representante da Força Aérea Real Britânica  os gamers estão na mira de grandes empresas e do exército para ocupar cargos relevantes  “a capacidade de assimilar informações  reagir rapidamente em situações extremas  coordenando ações enquanto se mantém o foco sob pressão  são atributos comuns aos jogadores profissionais de videogames”. Na onda dessa novidade  a empresa Game Academy viu nos jogadores a oportunidade de potencializar o uso dessas habilidades no ambiente de trabalho e futuramente podem  até constar nos currículos. "Os empregadores exigem liderança na hora de contratar  então  posso incluir no currículo meus anos liderando ataques no World of Warcraft!"  afirmou David Barrie  um dos fundadores da Game Academy.  O preconceito contra os gamers tem diminuído à medida que as empresas comprovam a eficiência de quem joga videogame em cargos de importância e trabalhos em grupos  Matthew Ricci  que joga EVE Online  basicamente já possuí um mestrado em administração de empresas. Como diretor de uma corporação com centenas de jogadores no game  há quatro anos ajuda marcas internacionais a ingressar no mercado canadense dentro dessa parceria. Ryan Gardner  diretor de recrutamento profissional  enfatizou que as habilidades sociais dos jogadores podem ser utilizadas em um ambiente profissional  como o trabalho em equipe  a resolução de problemas à curto prazo e o planejamento estratégico. Então  quando alguém disser que jogar não dá futuro  já sabe!  Life Is A Game! Via: David Molloy BBC  #progamer #gaming #game #ps4 #xboxone #nintendoswitch #pcgamer

Does anyone else Remember Minecade? Well  if you don't  then I can't say I blame you. Minecade was a server network that was popular in the Java edition of Minecraft for a short while. One of the most popular games on it was Super Craft Bross  which was basically Kit PVP with double jumping and special abilities. Sethbling  a Minecraft YouTuber who specializes in making mechanics and contraptions  was a pretty big face of the server for a while.  However  as time went by  things around the server started to go downhill. Updates for Super Craft Bros. were few and far between. Balancing issues and bugs were rarely if ever  fixed. To make things worse  Minecraft's popularity was in a lull. It was around this time I quit playing on Minecade because the games I liked just weren't fun to play anymore.  Fast forward to now. With Minecraft getting a bit of an extra life when it comes to mainstream popularity  I wondered what Minecade has been up to. Last I checked  they could barely break 50 players  and those players were mostly on a rather basic creative server. When I went to the website  all I found was  well  this. The website is a mess. I’ve also checked around a few forums and can’t find much.  So. What happened to Minecade? I’ll keep looking. #minecraft #videogames #videogame #game #gamer #gaming #playstation #ps4 #xbox #xboxone #pc #nintendo #nintendoswitch *puts on detective hat*

I’ve been steadily picking at 'Fire Emblem Three Houses' for the past month or so and while I admit I haven’t quite finished the game I can say confidently that it is one of my favorites of the year. While I don’t have a ton of experience with the Fire Emblem series it's hard to imagine the diehards finding too much at fault with it’s core gameplay. The turn based “rock paper scissors” battles the series is iconic for are so engaging and addictive to play and beautifully presented. There’s something so epic about having the camera rapidly zoom in to the ground level of the battlefield so you can watch your characters duke it out. But I think the crowning achievement of this game is its story and narrative structure. You play as “The Professor” a sort of blank slate character who finds him or herself teaching at a prestigious military academy. In between battles you will fill your time lecturing and getting to know your students (who of course are your soldiers in battles) all the while completing side quests around the school. It’s essentially a lighter but more focused version of what the Persona series does. Within the first couple hours of play I found myself really caring for my students and motivated to prepare them as effectively as I could so they wouldn’t die in combat (yes perma-death is still a thing if you want it). This along with a storyline that evolves and twists based on your actions and choices makes for an immensely satisfying narrative experience. Well  this was seriously the better part of three houses. It wasn't as good as blue lions but better than Rhea's route  definitely better. Characters were the same of course but with new game plus it was easier to improve their skills and power as well as the support ranks. The story was better 'cause we were the "bad appearing but actually good" guys instead of the other way around (where we fought for the actual villain basically... 'till we killed them too). The Final fight wasn't really satisfying (and way easier than in Rhea's route...)  this was probably the easiest boss fight in Fire emblem I even had... Except every boss fight in fricking Fates. I was also surprised (with an piece of disappointment) what this route did with Dedue  that was something Dedue would literally never do and I really didn't liked how the blue lions were showed. I'm glad that I saved Felix with recruiting him... And Ashe... And Lysithia from Golden Deers too. Speaking of  next and last route Golden Deers  I'm looking forward to the meme house. A LucasArts ficou famosa nos anos 90 por seus jogos de Point and Click e um dos títulos mais amados por todos foi o Grim Fandango. O jogo é derivado da comemoração mexicana do Dia de los Muertos  onde nosso protagonista deve descobrir quem está por trás de uma cadeia de corrupção no Mundo dos Mortos e é válido lembrar que esse foi o primeiro título em 3D lançado pela empresa. Em 2015 tivemos uma desmaterialização de Grim Fandango que incluía também legendas e dublagem em português do Brasil. Quem não teve a chance de jogar  fica a dica de um jogo divertido e com uma temática atípica nos videogames. #grimfandango #lucasarts #pointandclick #xbox360 #xboxone #microsoft #playstation #playstation2 #playstation3 #playstation4 #ps1 #psone #ps2 #ps3 #ps4 #sony #nintendo #nintendoswitch #switch #pcgamer #arcades #jogatina #gaming #videogames

Febbraio 2018: ritratto di una studentessa stanca e pendolare che si gode uno sprazzo di sole invernale in uno splendido parco di Reggio Emilia. Stavo seguendo le ultime lezioni frontali per il percorso di formazione insegnanti e contemporaneamente scrivendo la tesi e facendo avanti e indietro tra Modena e Parma per questioni burocratiche. Valgono le mie occhiaie come testimoni oculari di quanto ho dichiarato?  Nostalgia a parte  dedico questo ricordo a tutti gli studenti  dalla primaria all'università  che ogni giorno affrontano mezzi pubblici  tomi di milioni di pagine ed ore su ore di lezioni. Anche quando vorreste farcire il muro di testate  dare fuoco agli zaini e fucilare i vostri professori  ricordate sempre che vince chi la dura  non chi si arrende! E concludo dicendo che se ce l'ho fatta io  che sono la pigrizia fatta a donna  ce la possono fare tutti😂. Buona fortuna  sempre e comunque. August and September where full of events  but no matter how late it is from actual event  I will still post some impressions from #gamescom2019 Because there is nothing more precious than to stay true to the geek I am 😅 Unfortunately we did not manage to get into #cyberpunk2077 booth  the line you see is already 5-6 hour of waiting time... but what we managed to see and try out during these two days of #gaming: 1. Pagan Online - smth new for me from #wargaming 2. World of Tanks - our classic  it is already a tradition to visit the booth of this Belarusian gamedesigner :) 3. Humankind 4. Two point hospital - did u also play this gem on PS2 :B suuuuper fun 5. Darksiders Genesis 6. Watch Dogs Legion 7. Medieval - also a cute game from PS2 8. Hands-free gaming- see the video impression  your eyes control the game 9. Biomutant 10. Monkeyking And some other fun mini and not so mini games. Au loin  le cri d’une mouette résonne dans le ciel azur  comme pour faire écho à une ancienne promesse. . أكثر الشركات التي تدور حولها الشائعات، Rockstar Games وماهو مشروعهم القادم، هل هو Grand Theft Auto 6 أو Bully 2؟ - اخر الشائعات التي ظهرت على الإنترنت وبالتحديد موقع Reddit ذكرت بأن Grand Theft Auto 6 هي بالفعل تحت التطوير الكامل منذ ٢٠١٨ تحت الاسم الرمزي Project Americas، كما أشيع مسبقاً. - الاستوديو الذي يتولى تطويرها هو Rockstar North، بينما Rockstar India مسؤولون حالياً عن Bully 2 للجيل الحالي والقادم. - اللعبة تدور أحداثها في Vice City، والخريطة ستضم مدن ومستنقعات وجزر صغيرة وكبيرة، وستكون أفضل من Grand Theft Auto 5. كما سيكون هناك مهمات محددة في Liberty City - أسلوب اللعب سيكون شبيه بالجزء الخامس، لكن هناك اختلافات ستجعله مميز. تدور أحداث اللعبة في عدة فترات زمنية مختلفة واللاعب سيرى التغير الذي سيطرأ على المدينة والمركبات مع التقدم في القصة. - الطقس والتقلبات الجوية وتنوعها سيلعب دوراً كبيراً في هذا الجزء، لذلك توقع وجود صواعق، فيضانات، وأعاصير. - تماماً كالجزء الخامس، قرارتك واختياراتك هي التي ستحدد نهاية القصة. - كل هذي إشاعة، لكن شي جميل ودي يكون حقيقة، انتوا وش رايكم؟ 😍 . . . . . ‏#iMustPlay  #لعبة #العاب #قيمز #قميرز #تحدي #سوني #بلايستيشن #اونلاين #videogames #games #gamer #gaming #instagaming #instagamer #playinggames #online #instagood #xboxone #ps4 #sony #gta #gtaonline #rockstargames #play #playing #xbox #playstation4 #playstation

In un Q&A con i fan  il doppiatore Travis Willingham ha parlato  del Mjolnir abbandonato che compare nel primo trailer del gioco alla base del monumento dedicato a Captain America  spiegando:  Domanda: Vediamo un’immagine del martello di Thor abbandonato. La storia di Thor indegno è stata già esplorata in passato. Cosa rende questa versione unica e differente?  Risposta: Cap è l’unico umano che Thor reputa degno di sollevare Mjolnir  ed ha fallito. Non solo  i “mortali” stanno discutendo tra di loro e non riescono a tornare uniti senza il loro Capitano. Anche Thor non riesce ad assumere il suo ruolo. Farà quindi una scelta molto interessante che avrà conseguenze indesiderate che riecheggeranno per tutta la campagna e si svilupperanno completamente nella storia del gioco.  Il Dio del Tuono ha abbandonato l’arma dopo aver fallito e presumibilmente non si sente più degno di brandirla  scelta che potrebbe portare a una storia che vada a esplorare il significato del fallimento per l’eroe  oppure una sorta di adattamento dell’acclamata run The Unworthy Thor(Indegno Thor). Finally it's #backlogbattler time and this time it's Fist of the North Star Lost Paradise on PS4. A game where you play as Kenshiro in another non canon adventure where knowing characters does help. In the tutorial you take out Shin  then go to the city of Eden where you become it's protector. You befriend the captain of the guard  get a truck you can ride around the sandbox in  do odd jobs like bartending  healing and managing a host club. You get random battles with goons everywhere which build up exp. You get references to the anime and manga everywhere. It's a wander around fighty drivey smash people's skulls in affair that plays a lot like Yakuza. It's mindless and can rack up the time easily. It's a fun game and if you like the series you'll love it. If you allow things to get on top of you however the main story will take a back seat and you'll find yourself just wandering around or driving around the desert looking for people to kill and items to get in the wastes. It's a fun game and I think it's worth the £30 asking price. #sega #sony #gaming #gamer #retro #arcade #franchise #retrocollectiveeurope #pickups #3d #adventure #rpg #action #3d #atlus #fistofthenorthstar #hokutonoken #kenshiro #playstation #ps4 #gamestergram #videogames #gamersunite #gamecollector #gamersofinstagram #jackrabbitgamer

Pickpocketing is also interesting in this game. You have to get close to a person and while remaing undetected  reach into their pockets.  The timer at the start determines how many seconds you will get to rummage around looking for items. The longer you can hold out the longer you get to look.  As the timer goes up  depending on your skill and your marks various attributes  it gets more dangerous to keep rummaging. The background of the timer will start to turn red when you are close to getting caught.  Once you have completed the timer mini game successfully you use what time you have earned to go through the various items and uncover what they are. You pick what you want and then have to navigate to the exit.  You manage to do that before time runs out and you have successfully pickpocketed someone!  Protip: To level Pickpocketing up faster and easier  do it to people who are sleeping! . . . . . . . . . . #pickpocket #kingdomcomedeliverance #pickpocketing #kingdomcome #medieval #rpg #gaming #videogames #simulation #xboxgamepass #XboxShare #XboxOneX #gamepass #rogue #thief #stealing #ninjaskills

✨Ocarina Of Time MasterQuest✨ ———————————————————————- . [2003 - Gamecube CAN - Aventure] . 🇫🇷 Voici l’une de mes fiertés  en tant que fan de Zelda  dont mon top 1 JV Ocarina Of Time  une version devenue rare et atypique. OOT avait été porté sur Gamecube notamment en bonus avec Wind Waker  et dans une compile collector exclusive du club Nintendo  mais pas que. Je présente ici la version Canadienne de OOT + Master Quest  c’est à dire la version experte  difficile  du jeu original. Un nouveau challenge plus ardu pour les adeptes du jeu en quête de défi (monstres plus féroces  mode miroir permanent  santé faible etc.) Bref une pièce que j’ai eu le flair de rentrer il y a deux ans environ avant que sa cote ne s’envole  car il existe une version US only  moins rare  mais cette version CAN devient assez balèze à dénicher à prix honnête! Bref la passion du collectionneur c’est aussi ça  miser et investir sur des pièces en devenir  sur des pépites dormantes  et qui plus est  pour l’un de mes Set favoris : Zelda. . • Connaissez vous cette version de Ocarina Of Time? Quelle sont vos trouvailles les plus originales en rétro qui sont devenues ultra rares par la suite? . 🇬🇧 I’m very proud to have this uncommon Ocarina Of Time  Canadian version in my collection. It became pretty rare since few years  I bought it 2 years ago. OOT was adapted on Gamecube as a bonus game included in Wind Waker  but also on one gamein US and Canada with this compilation. I’m happy to possess Canadian one  espacially because OOT and Zelda is one of my most important collection’s target. Ah shit here we go again  Il 24 ottobre del 2004  il videogioco di azione Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas  sviluppato dalla Rockstar Games fu rilasciato per Playstation 2. Subito dopo il filmato di apertura  in cui il personaggio principale Carl "CJ" Johnson viene molestato e ricattato da degli agenti di polizia corrotti  il gioco inizia con lui che si ritrova in un quartiere ostile della città e dice: "Ah merda  eccoci di nuovo qui. Il posto peggiore al mondo  il paese di Rolling Heights Ballas. Non rappresento Grove Street da 5 anni  ma ai Ballas non gliene frega niente." La scena non ha avuto alcuna diffusione significativa online fino al 2015  quando venne ricaricata su YouTube e iniziò ad essere usata come immagine di reazione. Tuttavia raggiunse una ancora maggiore notorietà solo nel settembre del 2018  quando si diffuse su Reddit. Il meme è ad oggi ancora uno tra i più utilizzati. Sin dalla sua prima comparsa in forma cartacea  It è stato riconosciuto come un caposaldo del genere Horror se non il suo maggiore esponente.  Considerato il capolavoro di Stephen King  il libro scritto nel 1986 ha avuto la sua prima trasposizione cinematografica nel 1990  con una miniserie in due episodi che a sua volta è stata manifesto dell’horror per molti anni.  Ai giorni nostri però  l’eco del successo di It non si è spento  e a concludere il ciclo di remake cinematografici iniziato nel 2017 con IT: Chapter One  arriva puntuale il 5 settembre prossimo IT: Chapter 2  con il non semplice compito di chiudere ancora una volta il baule di ricordi e terrore riemersi nelle menti dei fan e dei neofiti che si sono avvicinati timorosi ai cinema per diventare amici dell’affabile Pennywise. GPU integrata Intel Gen12 con 96 Execution Unit avvistata su CompuBench - Le GPU integrate Intel Gen12  basate sulla nuova architettura Xe (che sarà il cuore anche delle GPU dedicate)  rappresenteranno per ammissione della stessa azienda un cambiamento epocale. L’ISA sarà profondamente rinnovata  ma allo stesso tempo Intel aumenterà probabilmente anche il numero delle Execution Unit (EU)  cosa che in casa AMD e Nvidia abbiamo visto essere sempre un buon modo per incrementare le prestazioni rispetto alle generazioni precedenti.  Il maggior numero di EU non è solo un’idea logica  ma in queste ore sembra essere qualcosa di più: su CompuBench è infatti passata una non meglio identificata GPU integrata Intel Gen12 con 96 Execution Unit  più delle 64 EU integrate nelle CPU Ice Lake con grafica Gen11 o delle 72 EU dell’Iris Pro P580 vista in alcune CPU Xeon del 2016.  Il numero è inoltre decisamente superiore rispetto alla UHD 630 con 24 EU integrata nelle CPU consumer più diffuse. BIONIC COMMANDO: In 1987 arcade gamers became special forces soldiers in order to infiltrate an enemy base and stop the launch of a devastating missile attack.  A classic action platform game from Capcom this is one of the coolest games of its time thanks to all jumping being removed in favour of using an extendable arm to move around the level. Febbraio 2018: ritratto di una studentessa stanca e pendolare che si gode uno sprazzo di sole invernale in uno splendido parco di Reggio Emilia. Stavo seguendo le ultime lezioni frontali per il percorso di formazione insegnanti e contemporaneamente scrivendo la tesi e facendo avanti e indietro tra Modena e Parma per questioni burocratiche. Valgono le mie occhiaie come testimoni oculari di quanto ho dichiarato?  Nostalgia a parte  dedico questo ricordo a tutti gli studenti  dalla primaria all'università  che ogni giorno affrontano mezzi pubblici  tomi di milioni di pagine ed ore su ore di lezioni. Anche quando vorreste farcire il muro di testate  dare fuoco agli zaini e fucilare i vostri professori  ricordate sempre che vince chi la dura  non chi si arrende! E concludo dicendo che se ce l'ho fatta io  che sono la pigrizia fatta a donna  ce la possono fare tutti😂. Buona fortuna  sempre e comunque. Microsoft non si fida dei produttori di SSD  la cifratura software di BitLocker sale in cattedra - Dall’introduzione del famigerato Windows Vista  i sistemi operativi di Microsoft integrano BitLocker  una funzionalità che consente di crittografare l’intera partizione del sistema operativo al fine di proteggere le informazioni. Il tipo di crittografia usata da Bitlocker – hardware o software – è impostata tramite Criteri di Gruppo. Se disponibile  si usa la cifratura hardware standard. Molti SSD e hard disk offrono (o dicono di offrire) infatti sistemi di cifratura dei dati  che dovrebbero svolgere in hardware il compito di BitLocker. Di conseguenza BitLocker lasciava campo libero alle tecnologie integrate nei controller  dando credito alle parole dei produttori e sgravando la CPU da un carico importante.  Il problema è che a volte i sistemi di cifratura hardware integrati non fanno ciò per cui sono preposti  e se lo fanno lasciano la porta aperta al furto di dati da parte di malintenzionati come emerso in passato. La primera entrega de Arc the Lad  una impresionante saga de juegos RPG táctico en el que quizá no muchos recuerdan  pero tuvo una gama muy robusta en su tiempo  quizá no llegó a tener la pegada y la fama como otras franquicias de su mismo género o del JRPG. Pero fue una de las mejores de la primera PlayStation de Sony. Siempre estaban las mismas críticas de siempre de "medios profesionales" Del ámbito  criticando que sus gráficos eran de una generación pasada  que no eran meritorios de estar en una consola mucho más potente. Pero fuera de críticas que no hacen más que ensuciar grandes juegos y hacer que muchos jugadores no disfruten o se embarquen en juegos desconocidos  la saga siempre se ha presentado en un diseño curioso al más puro estilo clásico  con una jugabilidad muy cercana a Bahamuth Lagoon o Fire Emblem. También hay que remarcar  que su fama fue tal que  decidieron crear una serie de anime basado en el videojuego  algo muy curioso  ya que realmente se acostumbra a ver una práctica contraria  crear un videojuego referente alguna serie o anime. Muy recomendado para los fans del JRPG  RPG táctico o gente que haya visto el anime y que desconocía que venía de una saga de videojuegos. - Recordad que la tienda de accesorios gaming  móviles  consolas y videojuegos y mucho más @patasys  me ha hecho su embajador  así que aquí tenéis mi link especial: www.patasystem.com/retrofantasy y las seis primeras personas que ordenen algo tendrán envió gratis con el Código FREESHIPPINGRETROFANTASY. ¡Ya me dirás si has encontrado algo de tu gusto!. - #retrocollective #retrogamer #retrogames #retrogamescollector #retrovideogames #retrogaming #retrocollector #videogaming #videogamescollective #videogamescollector #videojuegos #videogames #instagaming #instagames #instagamerspain #gaming #games #gamescollector #sony #playstation #manga #jrpg #anime

In 1993 I was at mates house with friends having a game night. We game all night  few beers  mosty multi player and always Mega Drive. Though this night was different. ============== Someone had taken along their Super Nintendo to show a game they had just purchased. My eyes rolled. I only play Sega games 🙄 so with pain I took honour of leaning over back of the TV and fishing to unplug the trusted Mega Drive. ============== Being a Sega fanboy I had yet to experience or even see a SNES game in action so my care level was probably zero. Yet my mind was soon to change and tbh it was easy. While we were all taking turns on a Super Mario level I could feel myself getting hooked.Then after playing the likes of Pilot Wings  Mario Kart and F-Zero...I was sold. ============= The very next day I hit the shops and picked up this very SNES  a copy of Super Mario All Stars ....and every Mode 7 game that I could get my hands on 😏👍 ============== Super Mario All Stars was the very first game I played on the SNES and I guess it made me never choose sides again. 😎🤝😎 ============ Was there ever a game that made you rush out and buy a console?? . . . . . . . . . #nintendo #snes #supernintendo  #supermario #supermarioworld #supermarioallstars #retrogamer #retrogamers #retrogaming #retrogamingcommunity #oldschoolgaming #videogames #gamecollector #gamerguy #instagamer #gamer #gamerlife #gaming #gamersofaus #aussiegamers #nintendopower #nin10do #nes #nintendolife #nintendogamer #nintendogaming

La GPU avrebbe 1408 stream processor capaci di raggiungere una frequenza di boost fino a 1645 MHz. Akumajou Dracula X: Chi no Rondo  AKA Castlevania: Rondo of blood.  The game was released in japan on oct 29th  1993. An amazing halloween gift for our Japanese buddies! And it wasn't released outside of Japan for almost 15 years. At some point it was considered the best Castlevania ever  and I think everyone thought alike until Symphony of the Night. So basically  a lost jewell for the western world. There was a remake in the SNES but it was actually a complete different game. It was possible to play it as an unlockable game in The Dracula X Chronicles... But now we are going to be able to enjoy the original game for the first time  on the Turbografx-16 mini!!! So  the first videos are an amazing intro animation. The voice translation is: "Long ago people lived in peace and harmony. No one noticed the looming shadow among them. Their senses clouded in darkness  evil ate away at their souls. In the late hour they congregate to call the powers of Satan with sinful blood to save them from their mortal existence. Evis has once again been made flesh. He can become a bat  fog  or wolf and feasts on human blood. Lord of darkness  master of Castlevania  Dracula walk among us." This game has a fantastic soundtrack  making use of the CD-Rom capacity for better sound quality. There's a 2CD OST released with music from this game and also from Castlevania Bloodlines. DDR4 a 5 GHz e Ryzen 9 3900X: l’overclocker der8auer testa un inedito kit di Gigabyte - L’overclocker Roman “der8auer” Hartung ha messo alla prova su piattaforma X570 con Ryzen 9 3900X un inedito kit di memoria DDR4-5000 di Gigabyte. L’azienda ci sta lavorando internamente da un po’ di tempo  tanto che all’ultima Gamescom di agosto aveva promesso a der8auer che presto gli avrebbe inviato qualcosa di speciale. Detto  fatto. Il regalo è arrivato e l’overclocker ha ovviamente messo tutto alla prova in un video che potete vedere qui di seguito. I moduli hanno funzionato a 5 GHz senza richiedere particolari interventi o raffreddamento esotici  ma solo l’impostazione di un semplice profilo XMP dal BIOS. Un ulteriore segno che  se ancora avevate dei dubbi  le piattaforme AMD ne hanno fatta di strada dai Ryzen di prima generazione nella compatibilità con le memorie.  I due moduli sono basati su chip Micron  soluzioni DDR4-3200 che di base richiedono 1 2 volt. É extremamente comum em um jogo você ter vários aspectos que se repetem  inimigos  objetos no cenário  itens e etc.  Por isso também é bastante comum nós podermos generalizar essas coisas e reutiliza-lás. … Pegue o exemplo de um personagem principal  ele vai estar EM TODAS AS FASES! Kkkk Agora imagine o fluxo -> Criar uma cena nova -> Colocar um SKSpriteNode -> Colocar a textura do personagem -> Seta as animações -> Os componentes -> Roda o jogo  Agora pense que seu jogo tem 30 fases distintas… Isso irá se repetir 30 vezes  kkkk.  Pior… Na 27 fase você percebeu que a escala podia ser melhorada  aumentar só um pouquinho  você terá que voltar em cada fase e ajustar isso  certo?  Pois bem  chega de fazer as coisas no Go horsing… trago a vocês a tal solução… SKReferenceNode Esse lindo  é um node que simplesmente é uma referência a uma outra cena! Então numa cena podemos fazer o personagem principal e em todas as outras 30 só referenciaremos ela. Relaxa que não pesa já que é só uma referência! E você também pode modificar a vontade dentro de uma cena específica se quiser algo especializado para tal cena  ou modificar na cena “mestre” e assim em todos os lugares que ela estiver sendo referenciada a modificação será aplicada! Per quanto possa essere un nuovo soulslike  Code Vein si conferma come un prodotto dall’anima originale e complessa  sfruttando l’estetica giapponese per proporre una delle esperienze più divertenti del genere. Attraverso a un sistema tanto accessibile quanto profondo e malleabile  vivere i panni di un Redivivo diventa una sfida più che gustosa che può essere adattata a qualsiasi tipo di giocatore. Ma il combattimento non è l’unico elemento invitante del gioco: la trama coinvolgente – anche grazie a un editor più che ottimo – e il ricco cast sono solo la portata principale di un mondo fatto di misteri  ricordi e colpi di scena sconvolgenti. Nonostante qualche comprensibile difetto  Bandai Namco e le menti dietro God Eater sono riusciti a produrre una nuova formula vincente  facendo nascere un’esperienza che si fa decisamente perdonare della lunga attesa.⠀ La mia Recensione di Code Vein per Game Division!⠀ -⠀ -⠀ #codevein #bandainamco #anime #vampire #soulslike #pc #ps4 #playstation #nintendoswitch #sony #xbox #mcirosoft #gamingfolk #gaming #gamer #game #videogame #videogames #videogioco #videogiochi #nerd #geek #singleplayer #multiplayer #player #playing #play #gamereview #recensione

Zelda Link’s Awakening – это ремейк классической Зельды с видом сверху  выпущенной ещё в далёком 1993 году на #GameBoy. На #NintendoSwitch игра перенесена практически с учётом всех нюансов  с улучшением графики и управления. Эта забота одновременно и плюс и минус игры. Бывалые геймеры будут рады и вспомнят былые времена  когда каждый секрет в подобных РПГ решался далеко не сразу и приходилось пробегать всю карту в течении нескольких часов  чтобы наконец понять  что и куда дальше. Но сегодняшние геймеры скорее назовут это проблемой геймдизайна  но никак не фишкой игры.  Что касается меня  то проблемы при прохождении я испытал буквально пару тройку раз. И это не проблемы с загадками в подземельях (они то как раз здесь очень крутые и их интересно решать именно самому)  а практически всегда это был вопрос «Куда же идти дальше?» Порой игра даёт лишь мелкие подсказки  которые не всегда очевидны. Решал это с помощью гайда для версии игры 1993 года (благо вся карта перенесена в ремейк 1 в 1) и зазрения совести от этого не испытываю. Пробегать всю карту и рубить мечом каждый кустик в надежде  что вот сейчас то под этим будет секретный вход в нужное подземелье… время дороже и времена не те :) В целом  ремейк однозначно понравился. Особо хочется отметить графику и стилистику проекта. Эстетика пластиковых игрушек выглядит замечательно  мир и персонажи очаровывают. #LinksAwakening способна вернуть вас в детство  даже если вы не играли в оригинал. А #Switch получил ещё один отличный эксклюзив в свою библиотеку.  #zelda #nintendoswitchgames #nintendo #linkzelda #portablegaming #rpggames #videogames #consolegaming #консольныеигры #видеоигры #обзорыигр #games #gaminglife

🎮 BARCODE BATTLERS II 時空を超えた戦士たち (Warriors who travelled in time) . Barcode Battlers was a series of Handheld consoles made by Epoch. . Barcode scanning toys and arcade games were extremely popular in the 90's Japan including the Datach Famicom add on  the later Digivices and Barcode Wars by Bandai. The strength of the Barcode Wars series was its connection to nintendo  allowing them to make exclusive barcode games with nintendo franchise such as Mario Bros and Zelda. . It also allowed players connect to their Super Famicom or original Gameboy via the 'Barcode Boy' to send data from the barcode cards into the Barcode Battler console games. . Barcode Battler was highly successful in Japan and even saw a release of western versions with alternative art and characters. . I finished Link's Awakening earlier on today (I dunno about you but you have to 100% everything before you can tackle the final boss  right?!) Just wanted to give my thoughts!  This is absolutely how a remake should be handled. I loved it from start the finish. I remember the art style throwing a few people when it was originally unveiled but I thought it was cute as hell then and thanks to the sound it makes when you dash with the Pegasus Boots I think it's even more cute now 😍 The soundtrack matches the chibi-esque style perfectly. However. The was one new feature that downright annoyed me... Dampe's dungeon creator. For anyone else who went ahead and completed the Gold Challenges  I have one word. Stairs. Good God. I'm not sure I can do this justice in text but you cannot (as far as I know) manually connect stairs to stairs. This made "Bows > Swords" really frustrating because the damn stairs just wouldn't connect to the ones I wanted them to connect with! It seems to connect stairwells to the ones closest so it's "easy" to work around but I shouldn't have to find a work around 😅 You could argue this was just an add on and has no real impact on the main game  and you'd be half right... some of the optional collectibles (heart/bottle/seashell) are locked behind Dampe's tutorials. You can also only use preexisting dungeon rooms... Which means you're replaying rooms from previous dungeons over and over again. With a little work and a bit more freedom I'm sure a Zelda Dungeon Creator would make a fantastic little eshop game but as it is now I'd give it little more that a "meh". BUT I DID LOVE THE GAME  HONESTLY. DON'T READ TOO MUCH INTO MY BITCHING ABOUT FUCKING STAIRS 😂  I probably should have started in Hero Mode because with the new addition of bottles the game was waaaaay easier. ------------------------------------------------ . . . . . . . . #retrocollectivena #retrocollectiveeurope #retrocollective #VideoGames #Gamer #retrocollective #retrogames #gamestagram  #instagaming #retro #gaming #collector #retrostyle #retrovideogames #retrocommunity #retrogaming #igersnintendo #zelda #thelegendofzelda #LinksAwakening #link #marin #switch #nintendo #WeekofZelda

Give me a moment to talk to Harding…” Abram cuts her off  “Clearing the West Road will help our soldiers gain a foothold of the crossing. We must do so now.” Cassandra resigns with a sigh  “Yes  we should go.” At the corner of her eye  she sees Lucian walking by. Cassandra  “Scout Durand!” Lucian jogs up to Cassandra and bows  “Seeker.” Cassandra  “Gather the others. We’re heading to the West Road. I just need to make a minor adjustment to my provision.” Cassandra  “Do what you must but do it quick.” “Yes ser.” Without a pause  Lucian dashes off. To prepare for the new Modern Warfare i started off with the one that kicked the series into new heights. Bare in mind I played the remaster version. This is a solid game even in today standards. A short but impactful campaign that has good Characters  great set pieces and tight gameplay. In terms of arcade action you can't get any better then this. The multiplayer is as good as it's always been with the creating a class and adding attachments and skins. There are problems of course. First off the loot box system is horrible. I hate it and screw Activision for putting it in here and screw them harder for making dlc maps for a remaster...dlc. Activision really don't care. And for me I played it through veteran and I get it. It's hardest difficulty but you do sometimes feel really unfair. I lost count how many times I'd fight the same enemy after a checkpoint restart and it always be random if I'd have time to shoot him or he'd snap to me and kill me quicker then I can aim down sight's. Our felt very unfair. Apart from that the game is great and set in stone a series that would make way for a generation of gamers. But what did you guys and gals think? Let me know and I'll see you guys... In the next post.  #game #Games #gaming #videogame #videogames #callofduty #callofduty4modernwarfare #callofduty4remastered
